Class TableSetting

  • java.lang.Object
    • builderPatternPackage.TableSetting

  • public class TableSetting
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains components like chair, centerpiece etc. Delegates the cost calculation to table components. Modifies the count per table of table objects.Contains Style as a data member

    Varada
